      • testNorm

        public void testNorm()
        Tests Arma.norm(Mat, int) and Arma.norm(Mat, String) for vectors by comparing the results for following vectors with a pre-computed ground truth. Vectors used:
        • Mat.zeros(10, 1)
        • Mat.ones(10, 1)
        • Mat.eye(10, 1)
